{"word":"κρύπτω","slug":"κρύπτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰρύπτω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ etym.\">etym.</a> complex] ‘keep from view’, <b>hide<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> things <b><a href='B:470 5:14'>Mt 5:14</a>; <a href='B:470 25:18'>25:18</a>, <a href='B:470 25:25'>25</a>; <a href='B:490 13:21'>Lk 13:21</a>.</b> Metaph. <b><a href='B:470 11:25'>Mt 11:25</a>; <a href='B:470 13:35'>13:35</a>; <a href='B:490 11:52'>Lk 11:52</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:490 18:34'>18:34</a>; <a href='B:490 19:42'>19:42</a>; <a href='B:580 3:3'>Col 3:3</a>; <a href='B:610 5:25'>1 Ti 5:25</a>; <a href='B:730 2:17'>Rv 2:17</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> <b><a href='B:650 11:23'>Hb 11:23</a>; <a href='B:730 6:15'>Rv 6:15f</a>;</b> of withdrawal from public view <b><a href='B:500 8:59'>J 8:59</a>; <a href='B:500 12:36'>12:36</a>;</b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> sense of assuming an undercover allegiance <el>ϰεϰρυμμένος</el> in secret <b><a href='B:500 19:38'>J 19:38</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κρυπτός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κρυσταλλίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}